display="inline"><![CDATA[f(x)]]></fr:tex> is a point in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[O]]></fr:tex>, which is open in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[Y]]></fr:tex>, there is some <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[r>0]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B_{r}(f(x))\subseteq  O]]></fr:tex>. Since <fr:tex
