display="inline"><![CDATA[\delta >0]]></fr:tex> such that <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f(B_{\delta }(x))\subseteq  B_{r}(f(x))\subseteq  O]]></fr:tex>. Then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[B_{\delta }(x)\subseteq  f^{-1}(O)]]></fr:tex> and therefore <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f^{-1}(O)]]></fr:tex> is open in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>

